{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"bae1b559-e6bb-401c-b3aa-102440f4b71e","content":"`.testsettings` files are **not supported** by modern MSTest v3. You need to migrate to a `.runsettings` file. Here's the mapping from your current config:\n\n| `.testsettings` setting | `.runsettings` equivalent |\n|---|---|\n| `TestTimeout` property | `<TestTimeout>` under `<MSTest>` |\n| Code Coverage DataCollector | `<DataCollectors>` under `<DataCollectionRunSettings>` |\n| `AssemblyResolution` / `useLoadContext` | No longer needed |","toolRequests":[{"toolCallId":"toolu_vrtx_01BU1ZkikpiV3s6WT8xqDr1x","name":"report_intent","arguments":{"intent":"Creating runsettings migration"},"type":"function"},{"toolCallId":"toolu_vrtx_01TBoPWMTRr88c6A8LabGgYK","name":"create","arguments":{"path":"/tmp/sv-e3777173e9144a5e934c969d0236effa/local.runsettings","file_text":"<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?>\n<RunSettings>\n  <RunConfiguration>\n    <!-- Timeout per test in milliseconds (was TestTimeout in .testsettings) -->\n    <TestSessionTimeout>30000</TestSessionTimeout>\n  </RunConfiguration>\n\n  <MSTest>\n    <!-- Per-test method timeout in milliseconds -->\n    <TestTimeout>30000</TestTimeout>\n  </MSTest>\n\n  <DataCollectionRunSettings>\n    <DataCollectors>\n      <DataCollector friendlyName=\"Code Coverage\"\n                     uri=\"datacollector://Microsoft/CodeCoverage/2.0\"\n                     assemblyQualifiedName=\"Microsoft.VisualStudio.TraceCollector.CoverageCollectorDataCollector, Microsoft.VisualStudio.TraceCollector, Culture=neutral\">\n        <Configuration>\n          <CodeCoverage />\n        </Configuration>\n      </DataCollector>\n    </DataCollectors>\n  </DataCollectionRunSettings>\n</RunSettings>\n"},"type":"function","intentionSummary":"create a new file at /tmp/sv-e3777173e9144a5e934c969d0236effa/local.runsettings."}],"interactionId":"80887d5d-bc7e-40da-8bde-a20355ded60e","reasoningOpaque":"","reasoningText":"The user has a `.testsettings` file which is the legacy format. Modern MSTest (v3+) uses `.runsettings` files instead. I need to explain the migration and create a `.runsettings` file that maps the old settings.\n\nLet me map the settings:\n1. **TestTimeout** (30000ms) → `<TestTimeout>30000</TestTimeout>` under `<MSTest>` or via `[Timeout]` attribute\n2. **Code Coverage data collector** → `<DataCollectors>` section in `.runsettings`\n3. **AssemblyResolution / useLoadContext** → No longer needed in modern MSTest\n\n\n4. **Deployment** → `<DeploymentEnabled>` under `<MSTest>` section\n\nNow I'll create the `.runsettings` file and update the `.csproj` to reference it.","outputTokens":736,"requestId":"A03A:14C0A3:1B3BFC4:1F275A8:69FE9E8A"},"id":"27ac5e2f-dea5-4123-b60e-a48055f88219","timestamp":"2026-05-09T02:40:22.155Z","parentId":"ffa72e69-5121-4e5e-ad38-0f14486b9965"}
